        "content": "<p>So like this? (it does not error for me)</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"cp\">#[pin_data]</span>\n<span class=\"k\">struct</span> <span class=\"nc\">Foo</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">a</span>: <span class=\"kt\">usize</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"sd\">/// Abc</span>\n<span class=\"cp\">#[pin_data]</span>\n<span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"k\">crate</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">struct</span> <span class=\"nc\">Bar</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"cp\">#[pin]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"k\">crate</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">f</span>: <span class=\"nc\">Mutex</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">Foo</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
