    {
        "content": "<p>This is the code I have that triggers it:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"sd\">/// The fields of `Process` protected by the spinlock.</span>\n<span class=\"k\">struct</span> <span class=\"nc\">ProcessInner</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">is_dead</span>: <span class=\"kt\">bool</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"sd\">/// Bitmap of deferred work to do.</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">defer_work</span>: <span class=\"kt\">u8</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"sd\">/// A process using binder.</span>\n<span class=\"sd\">///</span>\n<span class=\"sd\">/// Strictly speaking, there can be multiple of these per process. There is one for each binder fd</span>\n<span class=\"sd\">/// that a process has opened, so processes using several binder contexts have several `Process`</span>\n<span class=\"sd\">/// objects. This ensures that the contexts are fully separated.</span>\n<span class=\"cp\">#[pin_data]</span>\n<span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"k\">crate</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">struct</span> <span class=\"nc\">Process</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"k\">crate</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ctx</span>: <span class=\"nc\">Arc</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">Context</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"c1\">// The task leader (process).</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"k\">crate</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">task</span>: <span class=\"nc\">ARef</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">Task</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"c1\">// Credential associated with file when `Process` is created.</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"k\">crate</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">cred</span>: <span class=\"nc\">ARef</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">Credential</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"cp\">#[pin]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"k\">crate</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">inner</span>: <span class=\"nc\">SpinLock</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">ProcessInner</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"c1\">// Work node for deferred work item.</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"cp\">#[pin]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">defer_work</span>: <span class=\"nc\">Work</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">Arc</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">Process</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"c1\">// Links for process list in Context.</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">links</span>: <span class=\"nc\">Links</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">Process</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 358993735,
        "sender_full_name": "Alice Ryhl",
        "timestamp": 1684332476
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I fixed it by making <code>ProcessInner</code> pub(crate)</p>",
